headline.main: AXIS LINE SKIRTED; British Armored Forces 80 Miles Inside Libya -- Nazi Tanks Retreat

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Friday, Nov. 21 -- The British Eighth Army moved yesterday through German and Italian positions toward besieged Tobruk on the third day of the offensive in Libya, and it was announced today that Rezegh, ten miles from Tobruk's outer defenses, had been taken.
